						               													<description>Enter a Dark Fantasy where Perdition is overrun by demonic WitchBorn returned from the dead. WitchBorn tear their brothers and sisters apart with an insatiable blood lust. You number among a few roaming bands of survivors&amp;mdash;maybe all that is left of your kind!&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Build your own war clan of eight survivors to recover lost cargo in WitchBorn infested plains.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Then, sell your treasures in Asylum. A derelict cathedral known as &amp;ldquo;The Pit&amp;rdquo; was converted into a tavern and bazaar. Humans, Guild, Dwarves, Elves, and Orcs bustle with the air of a dark carnival since there are no WitchBorn here. And a Guild warrior named Blood Messiah fills tankards at the world&amp;rsquo;s last standing bar. Carouse, undertake quests, and brawl. No night in The Pit is ever the same.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Play continuing adventures competitively, cooperatively, or in solo play.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Enter Perdition is a story-driven miniatures skirmish. Use the supplied standup figures, your own miniatures, or expansion sets including Reaper Bones minis. The ever-changing stories are told by free web apps so no GM is needed. The Pit accessories include The Pit adventure book, 5 sheets of templates and pop-up figures, stands for the figures, and instructions on how to get the free app for The Pit.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Play with one to six war clans and battle to take your world back from The WitchBorn.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;</description>
